    {
      "id": "PopularPost324603",
      "post_content": "@Equinox523:   \nWeirdly enough, I think that the mercenaries could have had a chance if they'd not had to tap to activate their search ability. It wouldn't be too broken because they'd still pay mana to do it, but you could get out some of the weaker ones ([Cateran Persuader](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cateran Persuader)) and search out the cheapest creatures very quickly. The Rebels would have been able to slowly build up, the mercenaries would have been able to quickly spam weak creatures. The end result would be that Rebels would get big quickly, and Mercenaries would get meatshields quickly. I think that'd be kind of neat.  \n  \nAs it is though, there's no point to playing a large creature then searching up a smaller one.",
      "posted_by": "NARFNra",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost324603\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">@Equinox523: <br/>Weirdly enough, I think that the mercenaries could have had a chance if they'd not had to tap to activate their search ability. It wouldn't be too broken because they'd still pay mana to do it, but you could get out some of the weaker ones (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cateran Persuader\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cateran Persuader\">Cateran Persuader</a>) and search out the cheapest creatures very quickly. The Rebels would have been able to slowly build up, the mercenaries would have been able to quickly spam weak creatures. The end result would be that Rebels would get big quickly, and Mercenaries would get meatshields quickly. I think that'd be kind of neat.<br/><br/>As it is though, there's no point to playing a large creature then searching up a smaller one.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '324603'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy48472\">NARFNra</span>\r\n                                (6/28/2013 2:16:44 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
